         <note audience="external">
            <p>These materials relating to Lewis F. Powell's life come
            from a variety of miscellaneous sources and are collected
            by the Powell Archives. This collection should not be
            confused with the Lewis F. Powell Jr. Papers, Ms 001. The
            Powell Papers contain the documentation of Powell's life
            which he created and maintained.</p>
         </note>
      </did>
